Use the standard library
This is how to largest_prime_factor of n:
  Remember that factor is 2
  Remember that last is 1
  Remember that value is n
  Do this n times:
    When remainder of value and factor is 0, then:
      Remember that last is factor
      Remember that value is quotient of value and factor
    But, if not:
      Increase factor by 1
    End when
    When value is 1, then:
      Leave the loop
    End when
  End do
  The answer is last
Now you know